                </div>
                <div class="lable">Legal information cannot be updated due to security reasons. For assistance, please contact our technical support team at <a href="#">support@example.com</a> or call our hotline at +1-800-123-4567.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="container_title">Securuty</div>
            </div>
            <div class="container_line"></div>
            <div class="info_container">
                <div class="info">
                    <button id="passwordEditBtn">Update Password</button>
